{
  "stem": "20686.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Where, where is the mechanism to tell this?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because when I talk about it and write about it, all this comes back to me.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "All this comes back that a father was forced to hang his son.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And the father said, what can I do?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And the son said to him, come on.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "You do it.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And his father put his head in because he didn't-- couldn't, couldn't-- he couldn't hang himself.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "He said, we hang together.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now, those things are difficult to, to explain.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And the art of normal-- of normality, I, I-- you've got to be crazy to find language to tell this sort of story.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then I go on to say, 'I resolve to speak in verse.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Perhaps it would lessen my pain.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Or maybe the verse is my curtain to bleed and sustain.' [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "'Why had the murderer spared me?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My dear ones, oh God, what an end!",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Trapped in a bunker like mice, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] gassed and burned.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Or visions, horrors of horrors, companions of all my night, will I be forever hostage to devilish sights?'",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, those things-- [SIGHS] [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] every time I write about it, it's like a pilgrimage back into the dark and darkness.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I know the story has to be told.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I really don't know.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And, and, and, and language becomes a real obstacle.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And one of-- in my latest book, but let me first read you another page on this poem to give you an example what I-- the difficulties.",
      "word_count": 27
    }
  ],
